      </group>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-D44E5E6A-5A9E-4097-BB85-0A68CAA45DA4" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>This flow assumes that we will assign part numbers to masks and track them as inventory until either put into service (expensed) or sold to the customer.
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-16D20CA5-6CB7-44E0-BB57-26A91F4EBDA3" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>KDD: Mask Part Numbers
We will create part numbers by mask type.  Transactions will be at the type level (e.g., 5 of type 1, 3 of type 2) vs. individual masks.  Pricing and standard costs will be maintained at the type level
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <group categoryValueRef="sid-88c044cd-4e18-4ecc-a0d9-bc3cf48372e6" id="sid-4BF32276-7131-4DFC-8A4D-76911498B394">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#00FF00"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#339966" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text_name"/>
         </extensionElements>
      </group>
   </process>
